data.description: Check out this beautiful brick home in the desirable Southwood Estates neighborhood! This home is tucked into the neighborhood on a quiet, dead-end road in a great location of Lake City giving you quick access to 75. This home is truly move-in ready with many upgrades done in the last two years including the metal roof, hot water heater, HVAC, new windows, flooring, kitchen and bathroom remodels, fresh paint, and this amazing open butler's pantry. Check out this already thriving garden off your back patio and the black cherry trees out front.  So much to see, you'll have to come check it out for yourself!
